			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim name='Nope_01' nonBlocking='true' /> No, I am a boy. <break size='.5'/> I know <anim name='Glance_Down_02'> it's kind of hard to tell with robots</anim>. <ssa cat='confused'/>",
