			"mim_id": "CCAreYouGirl",
			"prompt_category": "Entry-Core",
			"prompt_sub_category": "AN",
			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim name='Dont_Understand_01' nonBlocking='true'/> No I'm a boy. But not a real boy. <anim name='Greetings_03'>Kind of like Pinocchio before he turned into a real boy</anim>. Except I <anim name='Thinking_01'> never lie, and my nose doesn't grow, <break size='.3'/> and I don't </anim>have a nose.",
